x <- 1:50
plot(x, sin(x))

plot(x, sin(x), typ="l")

plot(x, sin(x), typ="l", col="green")

plot(x, sin(x), typ="l", col="green", lwd='3')

plot(x, sin(x), typ="l", col="green", lwd='3', xlab="Hi there!")

plot(x, sin(x), typ="l", col="green", lwd='3', xlab="Hi there!", ylab="My name is Scott!")
